{"Id":486,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-mazhonggang","Author":"Ma Zhong Gang","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://alquran.cloud/api","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以天体和启明星发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"你怎能知道启明星是什么？"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"那是灿烂的明星，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"每人都有一位监视者[天使监视并记录人的善恶]。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"人应想一想自己是用什么造成的。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他是用一滴射出的精液造成的，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"那精液是从脊骨和肋骨间流出的。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他[安拉]的确能使他[死者]复活。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"在那日，一切隐秘之事[如善恶，拜功，斋戒等]都要受检验。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"他[人]无能为力，也没有任何援助者。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"以反复降雨的云发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"以裂开[让植物生长]的大地发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"这[《古兰经》]确是分辨真伪的言辞，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"这不是戏言。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"他们的确搞阴谋[谋害穆圣]，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"我也有计谋[对付他们的阴谋]。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"因此，你[穆圣]当宽延不信仰者，你当暂时宽延他们。"}]}